# StyleHouse

A modern fashion e-commerce platform built with **WordPress**, **WooCommerce**, and hosted on **Pantheon**.

StyleHouse is an online shopping platform that offers fashionable clothing, jewelry accessories, footwear, and lifestyle products. The website is designed to provide customers with a smooth, secure, and enjoyable shopping experience through an attractive interface, organized product categories, and responsive design.

