# Project Overview

StyleHouse was developed as an e-commerce website to demonstrate practical implementation of online business concepts using WordPress and WooCommerce.

The website allows customers to browse products, search for fashion items, view detailed product information, and purchase products through a simple and user-friendly interface.

The primary objective of this project is to create an online fashion store that combines attractive design with efficient e-commerce functionality while applying WebOps deployment practices using Pantheon.

---

# Objectives

The project aims to:

- Build a professional online clothing store.
- Provide customers with a convenient shopping experience.
- Showcase clothing and fashion accessories in an organized manner.
- Demonstrate practical use of WordPress and WooCommerce.
- Practice version control using Git and GitHub.
- Deploy and manage a website using Pantheon environments.

---

